{"tid":1728723,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"LIHKG Misic Awards 2019 (連登討論區最愛女歌手五強投票post)","createTime":"2019-11-17T03:52:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T14:21:52.000Z","uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d8b3f3a5a8b3bdc5d2ea6c8a7f8a9c7b9f662e67","tid":1728723,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:52:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>連登討論區最愛女歌手</strong></span> <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">五強投票</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TVfmHEg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTVfmHEg.jpg&h=5d1fa29b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女歌手五強片段<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/j7S8Lp4575k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fj7S8Lp4575k&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz3Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=2ab5773b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/j7S8Lp4575k</a><br />\n<br />\n五強男女歌手投票開始，於男女歌手獨立投票post，尋找所屬歌手歌名留言，並按下正皮，最終會計算「正負皮淨值」分數，並選出金銀銅獎。<br />\n<br />\n以下將會有五強的名字出現，每個留言一個，按照自己所屬喜好按下正皮或負皮投票，結果將會計算由正皮減去負皮的淨直，投票截止時間為11月20日，晚上11時59分，並隨即點算結果選出金、銀、銅、獎。<br />\n<br />\n感謝各位參與，亦請大家再移玉步到女歌手投票post進行投票，並於連登十大金曲post在20強內選出十強名單，同時誕生三甲獎項。"},{"pid":"08b2e3b9d02479ec4bfb4b40fe46b11fee3d2a2a","tid":1728723,"uid":125502,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:52:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">衛蘭</span>"},{"pid":"316aaee1ceb64db6f4b122c0dc7f970c60a66417","tid":1728723,"uid":48318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:53:17.000Z","msg":"投hk protest yes, 投no bts<br />\n<a href=\"https://time.com/person-of-the-year-poll-2019/?go=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2Fperson-of-the-year-poll-2019%2F%3Fgo%3Dtrue&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz3Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=922061ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://time.com/person-of-the-year-poll-20